'''Jonathan Mason''' is an [[England|English]] actor. He stars in the lead role of the 2005 version of ''[[Lassie (2005 film)|Lassie]]''.
He is most notable for the part of Joe Carraclough in ''[[Lassie (2005 film)|Lassie]]'' and as the roles of James, in ''Nits'' and Alistair Fury on ''[[The Revenge Files of Alistair Fury]]''.
He also had a minor role in ''[[Vincent (TV series)|Vincent]]'' in 2006. Jonathon currently studies at [[St. Bede's Grammar School]].
